title: North Esports is looking for a Diamond 5+ Top Laner

embed.description: The latest Tweets from North Esports (@NorthEsportsNE). Esports Gaming Organisation

body:
North Esports is looking for a D5+ Top laner to join our competitive Esports lol team! If you fill the criteria then please head to our twitter and swing us a message. Look forward to hearing from you :)

North Decos
Manager of North Esports
